I"c<p>Use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pgrep</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">kill</code> to kill processes in terminal.<br />
For example, to kill all the processes of <strong>BetterTouchTool</strong>:</p>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># -i to perform case-insensitive match</span>
<span class="c"># kill -&lt;signal&gt; &lt;pid&gt;</span>
pgrep <span class="nt">-i</span> bettertouchtool | xargs <span class="nb">kill</span> <span class="nt">-9</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
